    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration fans! This vehicle is the perfect budget-friendly project car, offering a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and build something special. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it serves as an excellent foundation for a full rebuild or a valuable donor for authentic parts. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
